{"tid":1136634,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍左拖之後覺得自己變到好黑人憎","createTime":"2019-05-03T06:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T06:50:49.000Z","uid":236690,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f026830073ca847796b2289bb7b1b27de15d4e5e","tid":1136634,"uid":236690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"自問未拍拖之前都算係個幾獨立嘅人<br />\n就算身邊嘅人出曬pool 自己仲係A0都覺得無咩所謂<br />\n曾經以為自己就算拍拖 都可以做到好獨立 好自由<br />\n真係投入左一段感情之後覺得自己越黎越玻璃心<br />\n成日都患得患失嘅感覺好難受 <br />\n本身都係個幾開朗嘅人 成日嘻嘻哈哈<br />\n但係唔知點解拍左拖之後成日發男朋友脾氣<br />\n其實真係唔想 亦都唔係唔愛佢 但係就係成日都忍唔住<br />\n覺得佢應該好攰 日日都要氹我<br />\n而我都日日因為亂發脾氣之後好內疚於是搞到自己都好攰<br />\n應該點做好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a0805ee7e3cad82a20fa7ee42422328686dd5c","tid":1136634,"uid":69872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"你做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死港女"}]}